settings.title: The Chill Story
settings.text:
For too long we’ve ignored the negative impact that fast and connected lifestyles have on our mind and body. Chill was created to address those issues by bringing people together and giving them the natural supplements they need to relax, unwind and enjoy the moment. 

So if you believe in the power of CBD and other functional ingredients, why not join us? Take some time for yourself and kick back with a satisfying smoke, try the sweet sensation of a gummy, or play by your own rules with a chew pouch. 

Worry less, feel more, love yourself, and choose Chill.

settings.title: Freedom
settings.text: Chill believes we can freely turn away from stress, anxiety and conflict. Only when we choose freedom can we experience a full and balanced life.

settings.title: Choice
settings.text: Choice is best made when we are free and can engage in the moment. In a Chill State of Mind we concentrate, think clearly and process the world in a way that creates relationship with one another.

settings.title: Chill
settings.text: We believe you can beat stress and live a happier, more fulfilled life by prioritizing your own wellbeing. If you want to calm down and relax, we believe that our products could help.

settings.title: Our values
settings.text: Chill was born in a valley beneath the Rocky Mountains where relaxation, self care and individuality are valued above all else.
